# Validate Non-Trivial Changes

After making non-trivial code changes, always run the following commands to validate:

```bash
npm run typecheck   # tsc -b
npm run test        # Vitest single run
npm run lint        # ESLint
```

All three must pass before considering the task complete. Once all checks pass, always create a git commit with a descriptive message summarizing the changes. Do not push to the remote.
